Page 2 = Contents / Chapters / Index
Page 3 = Exercise Instructions (ČÍTAJTE = Read / DOPLŇTE = Complete the exercise / etc) + Textbook Symbols meaning (posluchové cvičenie na CD1/nahrávka č 1 = Listen to CD 1 - Track 1 / etc)
Page 5 - 17 = Lesson 1 = Vitajte na Slovensku = Welcome to Slovakia ==========================================================================================================================
In the textbook, you can't copy and paste from the PDF (pages are images, can't select text) - So I will be getting my most of my vocab from the online course - Also writing to notebook
  1 - Šťastnú cestu Johanna = Happy Journey Johanna 
    Maj sa dobre mama = Be well mom
  2 - Nech sa päči = Let him take care (offer seat)
    Ďakujem = Thank you
  3 - Na zdravie = Cheers
  4 - Hovorite po slovensky = Do you speak slovak
    Áno = Yes
  5 - Hovorite po nemecky = Do you speak german
    Nie = No
  6 - Dobré ráno pán profesor = Good Morning Professor
  7 - Dobrý deň = Hello
    Dobrý deň Prosĺm = Hello. Please...
  8 - Nech sa päči = Let him take care (carry bag)
  9 - Dovidenia = goodbye
  10 - Dobrú chuť pani profersorka = Enjoy professor (giving lunch)
    Ďakujem Aj vám = Thank you too
  11 - Prepáčte = Sorry
    Nič sa nestalo = Nothing happened (No Problem)
  12 - Dobrý večer pani maliarová. Ahoj Janko = Good evening Mrs. Painter
    Dobrý večer slečna Šoltýsová = Good Evening Miss Soltysoda
  13 - Koľko máš rokov = how old are you
  14 - Dobrú noc, katka = Good night katka
    Aj tebe dobrú noc = Good night to you too
  15 - Prosim? = Hello (When Answering Phone)
    Ahoj Robert. Ako Sa Máš? = Hello Robert. How are you?
    Mám sa výborne = I'm doing great
    Mám sa dobre = I am good
    Mám sa zle = I am bad
  16 - Ako Sa voláte = What is your name
    volám sa Carlo = My name is carlo
  17 - Ako sa volás = What is your name
  18 - Teši ma = You make me happy
    Aj mňa = Me too
  19 - Na zdravie = Cheers
  20 - prepáč = I'm sorry
    Nič sa nestalo = Nothing happened
  21 - Dopočutia = They will hear (hanging up phone)
  22 - Ahojte = Hello
    Čau = Hello/Goodbye
  23 - Maj Sa = Have a good time
    Čaute = Hello/Goodbye
  24 - Pekný deň Zuzka = Good day Zuzka
    Aj tebe Robo = You too Robo
  25 - Ano = Yes
    Nie = No
  26 - Ruzimiete po slovensky = You speak Slovak
Page 8 = Lesson 1: Questions:
  A) Nech sa päči = Let him take care (offer seat)
  B) Na zdravie = Cheers 
  C) Nech sa päči = Let him take care (give item)
  D) Prepáčte = Sorry
    Nič sa nestalo = Nothing happened (No Problem)
  E) Na zdravie = Cheers
  F) prepáč = I'm sorry
    Nič sa nestalo = Nothing happened
Page 9 = Alphabet = Slovenská abeceda / Vokály = Vocals(Vocabulary)
A, Á, Ä, B, C, Č, D, Ď, DZ, DŽ, E, É, F, G, H, CH, I, Í, J, K, L Ĺ, Ľ, M, N, Ň, O, Ó, Ô, P, Q, R, Ŕ, S, Š, T, Ť, U, Ú, V, W, X, Y, Ý, Z, Ž
a, á, ä, b, c, č, d, ď, dz, dž, e, é, f, g, h, ch, i, í, j, k, l, ĺ, ľ, m, n, ň, o, ó, ô, p, q, r, ŕ, s, š, t, ť, u, ú, v, w, x, y, ý, z, ž
























